title: Peanuts v2 00-16 + Ex (2012- |Digital|Empire+theGroup)
description:
These wonderful new editions to the Peanuts library for Kaboom! Comics are a mix of reprints and new material by a variety of noted writers and artists. The series is currently ongoing and this torrent collects all issues released so far, 00-16. I have added quite a lot of interesting, funny and just plain strange extras, which are the following:

-A Peanuts Halloween (2008) (c2c) (Team-DCP)
-Adventure Time/Peanuts Free Comic Book Day Edition (2012) (c2c) (Flipbook) (ArtNet) [the "flip" part of this has been correctly inverted to display right side up in a comic book reader]
-Complete Peanuts v1 (1950-1952) and v2 (1953-1954) [gotta love the classics!]
-Flying Ace Part 01-03 Digital Edition (2013) (digital-Empire)
-Unseen Peanuts
-Public Health Service Publication 1770 - Security is an Eye Patch (1968) (Peanuts) (ep.tc) [???]
-Trip Through the Des Moines Register and Tribune with Peanuts [?????]

The main issues are all digital editions thanks to Empire and theGroup. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
